{"tid":1287163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想聲援武漢嘅同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-05T05:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T13:46:15.000Z","uid":12426,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c186b390e85bbdfcda48c2db7a4e71201877d827","tid":1287163,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n武漢暴亂只不過係不滿興建焚化爐<br />\n佢地唔係為民主而上街<br />\n<br />\n兄弟們唔好見到中國有暴亂就開心打晒飛機要去聲援<br />\n人地無講過要香港人出聲<br />\n佢地淨係想習主席打救佢地咋！！！<br />\n<br />\n中國國力都仲係好強盛  唔好見到武漢有人上街就覺得中國有內部問題<br />\n你地睇下新彊西藏   就算之前有幾多自殺襲擊<br />\n而家一樣被中共管理得貼貼服服<br />\n<br />\n香港能跑出係因為有基本法同國際地位<br />\n中共先對香港人咁容忍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求大家7月7集中火力<br />\n力爭五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算你地有人係大中華膠<br />\n都必先救港才能救國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要被分化<br />\n香港人<br />\n加油！</span>"},{"pid":"924b3a514207c8dfb012a92a4e0580cecdc1db8d","tid":1287163,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0700aab97a7bcde476d293887538c955f47f0a82","tid":1287163,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:56:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2e7db57b50054f5fdf3f6bb89993b9c0a2c1d2b4","tid":1287163,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2fbc1db6cfb5bc2e3e10e4021cbfdb5efaf64dc","tid":1287163,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":