1287163,"uid":49228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權責任<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n77請集中五大訴求"},{"pid":"5ee49a2684276379cd0e3cdbfcd089333561c382","tid":1287163,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:51:15.000Z","msg":"唔好俾人分化到<br />\n冇人話要反攻大陸<br />\n只係要燒佢後欄<br />\n不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtoEwdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtoEwdk.png&h=45ccf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Np0Z6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Np0Z6F.png&h=d451cb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/05/145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png&h=2adf7012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43fe51a2a1c256bfa122dfcd1524c40013f6e333","tid":1287163,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"11c49ca1dd83ac4c42316199b458c762ef4d23ab","tid":1287163,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4782702b970fb6dfcbecb194b497d01248ebd098","tid":1287163,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:25:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e98dda7030b886727612d978d8d76ff6d18c05b2","tid":1287163,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa2462f712e28dec30abbb02ada4f26fd95514f1","tid":1287163,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c650da5df3775ab9330aa168d4a0769